name: Pasar Malam 1: Humble Realm of an Indonesian Police Officer #1
description:
Pasar Malam [Night Market] Series is a collection of photographs taken with phone’s camera in a Night Market. In this series, I’m bringing a humble realm of the subjects and the objects they re interacting/passing through.

Humble Realm #1 took a pic of a Police Officer standing by and looking around a pirated DVDs stall in a daily night market in Bali.
